column5: I have heard some very positive things about this lodge and was wondering if one knew if they have web site or a phone number. Thank you very much, Rog
Would you by chance be referring to Happy Days Lodge on lake Windermere ?
Happy Landing Lodge is a fish factory.call and get a brochure at 800-766-0876
I Own Happy Landing Lodge, You can check out our web site at www.happy-landing-lodge.com or you can call me direct at 1-800-766-0876.
